 "762 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/474586845"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItoLC6uumr4NAEAMaCDY3NzQzOTk2IISm7ocGMFU47wxABHIJNDc0NTg2ODQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1630397566.2186446", "card_id": "Q_483577251", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 261}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "网传阿里将解雇 10 名外泄内网文章员工，事件真实性如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "知情人士透露，阿里巴巴将对外泄露控诉前公司经理性侵内网文章的 10 名员工解雇。 因涉及讨论内部事务要求匿名的知情人士透露，阿里巴巴上周对内宣布，针对周姓员工在内网发帖控诉遭前公司经理侵犯的文章被对外公开之事，公司已将泄露这篇文章的员工开除。知情人士说，这些员工将周某内网控诉文章的截图除去带有个人 ID 的水印后对外公开发布，此等行为违反了公司政策。知情人士补充道，另外三人因在公共论坛发表不当评论而受到批评。 本月周某在内网控诉遭阿里巴巴前经理性侵的文章被迅速疯传，并引发了职场性别歧视的热议。阿里巴巴已将涉事经理开除，并接受了两位公司高管的引咎辞职。网传阿里解雇 10 名外泄内网文章员工！发生了什么？_ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-cac21d0ca777606acf1ecb4561f53316_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "721 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/483577251"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItoLC6uumr4NAEAMaCDY5NzQzNTM4IP/xsokGMDA46gdABXIJNDgzNTc3MjUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1630397566.2192032", "card_id": "Q_483504786", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 158}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待丹麦宣布不再视新冠为一种危害社会的疾病?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "消息称丹麦已经实现群体免疫，所以直接宣布无视新冠了？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-2d9ec3f1b97c00e3e21f4675b130ac80_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "657 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/483504786"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItoLC6uumr4NAEAMaCDY5NzI3Mzk5ILDssYkGMDc4rgRABnIJNDgzNTA0Nzg2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1630397566.2196767", "card_id